description:
The Wild Floral print inspired by the rolling plains of the Swiss Alps is printed on a beautiful sand textile. The Black Cotton Linen fabric backing has a concealed zip and finished with a one centimeter stitched edge, the cushion then fits a 50×50cm inner.

To make you this special cushion, 100% linen cotton blend fabric is first hand screen printed in Australia as a yardage print, and then cut by hand so that each product differs slightly in print layout. It is then hand sewn also in Australia and packaged up just for you.
